title: White Beeches Country Club
text:
The White Beeches Golf and Country Club is located in <a href="Haworth%2C%20New%20Jersey">Haworth, New Jersey</a>, USA, and has 18 holes of <a href="golf">golf</a>. It has hosted <a href="U.S.%20Open%20%28golf%29">U.S. Open</a> sectional qualifiers, Met Open qualifiers and the State Open. 
History.
The course was built in 1918 and designed by <a href="Walter%20Travis">Walter Travis</a>. It plays to a par 72 from about 6,500 yards.
It hosted its second annual <a href="American%20Junior%20Golf%20Association">AJGA</a> tournament last summer. 
The head professional is the ex-tour player, <a href="Jim%20McGovern%20%28golfer%29">Jim McGovern</a>, and the assistant professional is Bryan Romagnoli.
